	  </li>

	  <li>
	    <p>
	      Use the dot products you just found to evaluate:
	      <ol marker="1.">
		<li>
		  <p>
		    <m>\len{\uvec}</m>.
		  </p>
		</li>
		<li>
		  <p>
		    <m>(-5\uvec)\cdot\vvec</m>.
		  </p>
		</li>
		<li>
		  <p>
		    <m>\uvec\cdot(-3\vvec+2\wvec)</m>.
		  </p>
		</li>
