		  <p>
		    <m>\uvec\cdot(-3\vvec+2\wvec) = -3(1) + 2(-6) =
		    -15</m>
		  </p>
		</li>
		<li>
		  <p>
		    <m>\frac1{\len{\uvec}} = \threevec{1/3}{-2/3}{2/3}</m>
